OL,3,CFirst Minister 'sorry' for damage to
OL,4,Ccharity as she faces MLAs on McMonagle
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's First Minister
OL,8,FMichelle O'Neill has said she is
OL,9,F"deeply sorry" for damage caused to
OL,10,Fthe reputation of a charity which
OL,11,Femployed a former Sinn Fein press
OL,12,Fofficer who was under investigation
OL,13,Ffor child sex offences.
OL,15,FMs O'Neill faced MLAs in the Stormont
OL,16,FAssembly as she was questioned over
OL,17,Fthe ongoing controversy around how she
OL,18,Fand her party handled allegations
OL,19,Fagainst Michael McMonagle.
