OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe First Minister's comments came
OL,8,Fshortly after deputy First Minister
OL,9,FEmma Little-Pengelly distanced herself
OL,10,Ffrom Sinn Fein's "attempts to blame
OL,11,Fother organisations" in the fallout
OL,12,Ffrom the row.
OL,14,FIt also followed Assembly confirmation
OL,15,Fthat McMonagle was employed by Ms
OL,16,FO'Neill and three other Sinn Fein MLAs
OL,17,Facross two periods, when his salary
OL,18,Fwas paid for by Assembly allowances
OL,19,Fprovided from the public purse.
