OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FLast month, McMonagle, 42, from
OL,8,FLimewood Street, Londonderry, admitted
OL,9,Fa series of offences, including
OL,10,Fattempting to incite a child to engage
OL,11,Fin sexual activity. He will be
OL,12,Fsentenced in November.
OL,14,FHe was first arrested in August 2021
OL,15,Fand Sinn Fein has said it suspended
OL,16,Fhim as soon as it became aware of the
OL,17,Fpolice investigation.
OL,19,FHis term of employment with Sinn Fein
OL,20,Fat the Assembly formally ended in July
OL,21,F2022.
