OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FMcMonagle then went on to get a job
OL,8,Fwith the British Heart Foundation
OL,9,F(BHF), which did not know he was under
OL,10,Finvestigation for child sex offences.
OL,12,FSinn Fein has been under mounting
OL,13,Fpressure after it emerged that two
OL,14,Fformer party press officers provided
OL,15,Freferences for McMonagle in 2022 for
OL,16,Fthe BHF job.
OL,18,FThe press officers quit more than a
OL,19,Fweek ago after Sinn Fein began
OL,20,Fdisciplinary proceedings against them.
