OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FFollowing days of headlines, Stormont
OL,8,FSpeaker Edwin Poots selected an urgent
OL,9,Fquestion from DUP MLA Diane Dodds
OL,10,Fwhich asked if the furore had
OL,11,Fdiminished confidence in the First
OL,12,FMinister's office.
OL,14,FMs O'Neill said: "As a mother and as a
OL,15,Fgrandmother, I assert my absolute
OL,16,Fdetermination, both political and
OL,17,Fpersonal, to protecting all children
OL,18,Fand to protecting all other vulnerable
OL,19,Fpeople."
