OL,7,FShe then set out the sequence of
OL,8,Fevents which led to the resignation of
OL,9,Fthe two press officers ` Sean Mag
OL,10,FUidhir and Caolan McGinley ` as she
OL,11,Fsaid "legitimate concerns" had been
OL,12,Fraised.
OL,14,FShe told the Northern Ireland
OL,15,FAssembly: "In August 2021, when
OL,16,FMichael McMonagle informed Sinn Fein
OL,17,Fof his arrest and questioning
OL,18,Fconcerning serious criminal offences,
OL,19,Fthe party took decisive action.
