OL,7,F"In line with our child protection
OL,8,Fpolicy and human resources handbook,
OL,9,Fhe was immediately suspended from
OL,10,Fparty membership and his position as a
OL,11,Fpress officer with his employment
OL,12,Fterminated in June 2022 when his
OL,13,Fcontract ended.
OL,15,F"I was made aware of his suspension
OL,16,Fand I had no further contact with him."
