OL,7,FMs O'Neill repeated her insistence
OL,8,Fthat she did not know McMonagle had
OL,9,Fattended a Donate for Daithi event at
OL,10,Fwhich she was present in February 2023
OL,11,Fhosted by the British Heart Foundation.
OL,13,FShe said: "My sole focus was on Daithi
OL,14,F(Mac Gabhann) and supporting the
OL,15,Ffamily through the works of the
OL,16,Fcampaign and I was not aware that
OL,17,FMichael McMonagle was at this event,
OL,18,Fand I had no knowledge either that he
OL,19,Fhad gained employment with the British
OL,20,FHeart Foundation."
