OL,7,FMs O'Neill then told MLAs she had
OL,8,Fsince established that the charity had
OL,9,Fcontacted her party's then HR manager
OL,10,Flast year, after McMonagle was charged.
OL,12,FShe said: "This contact from the
OL,13,FBritish Heart Foundation was not
OL,14,Fbrought to my attention or the Sinn
OL,15,FFein leadership at that time, and that
OL,16,Fwas a serious omission.
OL,18,F"Members will know that I spoke with
OL,19,FFearghal McKinney, the head of the
OL,20,FBritish Heart Foundation, to discuss
OL,21,Fthis situation.
