OL,5,Crow
OL,7,F"This is an organisation that does
OL,8,Fsterling work providing support,
OL,9,Fresearch and obviously, services, and
OL,10,FI am deeply sorry for the reputational
OL,11,Fdamage caused to the British Heart
OL,12,FFoundation, and I regret that this has
OL,13,Fhappened, and I apologise for this."
OL,15,FShe added: "I want to be very, very
OL,16,Fclear that the issue of child
OL,17,Fsafeguarding is of paramount
OL,18,Fimportance to me and I will do
OL,19,Feverything that I can to ensure that a
OL,20,Fsituation like this never arises
OL,21,Fagain."
