OL,7,FSinn Fein leader Mary Lou McDonald
OL,8,Fsaid she "deeply regrets" that a
OL,9,Fcharity has been caught up in a
OL,10,Fscandal involving a former party press
OL,11,Fofficer.
OL,13,FMs McDonald said: "There must always
OL,14,Fbe accountability for wrongdoing.
OL,16,FThat is why when I was made aware of
OL,17,Fthis issue on Wednesday, 25th
OL,18,FSeptember 2024, decisive action was
OL,19,Ftaken.
